<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"50%","style":{"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:50%"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">How can we help you?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {"width":"50%"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:50%"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>       Stepping out into the vibrant, pulsing world as an openly gay individual is a transformative experience, a boundless journey where every interaction and encounter thrills the senses just as much as the final, hard-won destination.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>       This is a journey of self-discovery, of reclaiming your narrative, of stepping boldly into the light and declaring, without hesitation or apology, "This is me, in all my glorious, unapologetic queerness." It\'s a path that may at times be challenging, but one that ultimately leads to a profound sense of liberation, of community, of living each day to the fullest as the vibrant, multifaceted individual you were always meant to be.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Feel free to contact us!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/contact-form {"subject":"Contact form submission","className":"is-style-animated"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-jetpack-contact-form is-style-animated"><!-- wp:jetpack/field-name {"label":"First name","required":true,"requiredText":"(required)","width":50,"borderRadius":5} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/field-name {"label":"Last name","required":true,"requiredText":"(required)","width":50,"borderRadius":5} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/field-email {"required":true,"requiredText":"(required)","borderRadius":5} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/field-textarea {"requiredText":"(required)","borderRadius":5} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:jetpack/button {"element":"button","text":"Submit","width":"","align":"center","lock":{"remove":true}} /-->